             was indicted for <rs id="t17870221-46-off232" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17870221-46-off232" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17870221-46-off232" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>
               burglariously and feloniously breaking and entering the dwelling house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17870221-46-victim583" type="victimName">
                           Ann 
                           Evans
                        <interp inst="t17870221-46-victim583" type="surname" value="Evans"></interp>
