                        <interp inst="t17870221-46-victim583" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                     </persName>
                     
                  , about the hour of six in the night, on the <rs id="t17870221-46-cd233" type="crimeDate">9th day of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17870221-46-off232 t17870221-46-cd233"></join>, and burglariously stealing therein, one cloth jacket, value 12 s. a bed gown, value 6 d. an apron, value 6 d. a hat, value 6 d. one half crown, value 2 s. 6 d. and 2 s. 6 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17870221-46-victim585" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
                     Jones
                  <interp inst="t17870221-46-victim585" type="surname" value="Jones"></interp>
